 and Dominic (our CTO), to nearly 10 people now.\r\n\r\nPeter Lynch once said, “Owning stocks is like having children - don\'t get involved with more than you can handle.”\r\n\r\nTradeHero has, hopefully, come to the rescue.\r\n\r\nThat’s all for now – stay tuned for updates!','Welcome to TradeHero’s Official Blog','','publish','closed','open','','welcome-to-tradeheros-official-blog','','','2013-06-21 15:59:46','2013-06-21 07:59:46','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?p=86',0,'post','',0),(87,4,'2013-06-13 15:54:19','2013-06-13 07:54:19','Hey there,\n\nToday marks the <i>x</i>th month since our launch on the 12<sup>th</sup> of December, 2012!\n\nOn this blog, we’ll be posting updates, stock market news &amp; tips, articles, information on TradeHero and much more. Check it out regularly for the latest news.\n\nWe’ve had an incredible <i>x</i> months. TradeHero’s up for its 2<sup>nd</sup> round of seed funding. Investors have generously responded and we’re on the right track. We’ve been contacted by people from all over the globe telling us that they love this app. If you’ve enjoyed our app so far, rate it on the App Store or let us know on Facebook (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/TradeHero\">www.facebook.com/TradeHero</a>), Twitter (@TradeHeroMobile) or email us (<a href=\"mailto:support@tradehero.mobi\">support@tradehero.mobi</a>).\n\nThat said, if you have some improvements in mind, feel free to contact us as well. We’ve received some great feedback along the way that has helped us tremendously. We know that some of you have asked us to include your local stock exchanges (Mexico and India, we hear you!) Don’t worry; we’re on it. We’re excited about the release of our Android version too.\n\nBehind every Trade Hero are the unsung heroes, the team from Singapore that has been working tirelessly to bring you this app. Our team in Singapore has expanded from 2 in early 2012, comprising Dinesh (our CEO) and Dominic (our CTO), to nearly 10 people. You’ll hear more about