2,1,'2013-06-15 21:15:15','2013-06-15 13:15:15','<a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/top10.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" alt=\"top10\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/top10.png\" width=\"750\" height=\"250\" /></a>\r\n\r\nYet another achievement unlocked! TradeHero represented Singapore in the Echelon 2013 Tech Conference Asia held recently on the 4<sup>th</sup> and 5<sup>th</sup> of June at the Singapore Expo.\r\n\r\nWe also emerged as winners alongside iCarsClub at Echelon Satellite Singapore held 2 months before the actual conference.\r\n\r\nTradeHero has indeed come a long way.<!--more-->\r\n\r\nWe first joined the pitching at Echelon Satellite Singapore alongside 19 other startups, hoping to qualify to the finals. Emerging as winners together with iCarsClub, we were chosen to represent Singapore in Echelon 2013.\r\n\r\nWe pitched at the conference to over 2,000 entrepreneurs and investors.\r\n\r\nCheck out our pitch at Echelon 2013 done by our CEO, Dinesh here: <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8A6b3tnF49Y\">Pitch at Echelon (TradeHero)</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-2013-06-14-at-2.51.09-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-156\" alt=\"Pitching at Echelon 2013\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-2013-06-14-at-2.51.09-PM.png\" width=\"599\" height=\"594\" /></a>\r\n<i>Dinesh pitching at the conference (above) </i>\r\n\r\nDinesh was also interviewed during the conference. Do check out his interview here: <a href=\"https://www.vimily.com/share/wiJtT6ZjczX\">Interview with Dinesh</a>\r\n\r\nThe TradeHero team would like to thank Echelon 2013 for giving us this opportunity. We will continue working towards greater achievements to bring an even better Hero experience for everyone. Stay tuned!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>The 10 pitching companies at Echelon 2013</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Echelon-2013-pitching-startups.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-168\" alt=\"Echelon-2013-pitching-startups\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/Echelon-2013-pitching-startups.png\" width=\"560\" height=\"412\" /></a></p>\r\n<em>A little information about <strong>Echelon</strong>:</em>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Echelon is a major Asian tech startup conference that gathers the best regional startups held annually. This year, Singapore had the privilege in hosting the event.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Over 100 companies around Asia pitched at the 9 satellites that were held, and 10 finalists were shortlisted by their professional team.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>For more information, do visit their website at <a href=\"http://e27.co/echelon/\">http://e27.co/echelon/</a></em>','TradeHero at Echelon 2013: Top 10 Promising Startups in Asia','','inherit','closed','open','','154-revision-24','','','2013-06-15 21:15:15','2013-06-15 13:15:15','',154,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/154-revision-24',0,'revision','',0),(223,1,'2013-06-15 21:07:34','2013-06-15 13:07:34','<a href=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/blog3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-178\" alt=\"blog3\" src=\"http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/blog3.png\" width=\"750\" height=\"250\" /></a>TradeHero has been featured on some of our users’ blogs.\r\n\r\nHere’s a short recap of the reviews that we’ve received so far:\r\n<ol start=\"1\">\r\n	<li><strong>BigFatPurse</strong>: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">http://www.bigfatpurse.com/2013/01/review-of-tradehero-virtual-vs-reality/</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n“TradeHero is easy for anyone to participate and accessible on-the-go with your phone.”\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li><strong>Marubozu</strong>: <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">http://mystocksinvesting.com/trade-hero/follow-my-trades-at-tradehero